### POST /api/v1/trips/{id}/cancel
### Descripción: Cancelar viaje. Requiere JWT (pasajero, conductor o admin) + X-Tenant-Id.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>, X-Tenant-Id: <guid>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TripDto) | 403 | 404 | 422

# @name cancelTrip
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips/{{TRIP_ID}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Cancelado por pasajero"
}

### Response esperado (200): TripDto
### Response error (422): INVALID_TRANSITION, etc.
